cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with crowd density and count estimation using deep neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed model also involves multi-task learning (cs.AI) and convolutional neural networks (cs.NE), which are commonly used in computer vision and machine learning. Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed model on two datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
